Crossword Puzzle Infos

Arizona is a US state with Phoenix as its capital. Phoenix is the largest city in Arizona and the fifth most populous city in the United States. It is located in the southwestern region of the country and is known for its desert climate and hot summers. Arizona is home to many national parks, monuments, and other attractions, making it a popular tourist destination.
